heisigStory: Wheat . . . elbow. Like the characters for I (Frame 17) and ego (Frame 690), this kanji is also representative of the subject, with the special connotation of privacy.
koohiiStory1: Warning sign: "Private wheat, trespassers will be elbowed".
koohiiStory2: I already know this as watashi, or "I". In order to associate the keyword of private, I´ll think of this one as "Private I", like a detective.
myStory: chữ Tư. riêng, bí ẩn. hoà và chữ khư.
